name: Warmup_Div05_Sub04
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD5S4.CPF,
GmailD5S4.NOME,
GmailD5S4.EMAIL,
GmailD5S4.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S4.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD5S4.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD5S4.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S4.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV05_SUB04 GmailD5S4
UNION
